item.title: Casting CAST
item.description: The general consensus was that no one’s husband thought they should be there. With a theme like “Busyness”, it’s hard to find a woman who can speak to the topic as an expert at managing it. And even if she does exist, none of us could relate to her, which was what the event was about. These women were sitting in confession via a stage in front of a couple dozen of their sisters.
